name: One Bowl Cinnamon Cake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180C. Lightly grease and line a 20cm cake tin with baking paper and set aside.
Sift both the 1cup of self raising flour and the extra 1 1/2 tablespoons and cinnamon into a large bowl.
Add sugar, eggs, milk and vanilla and pour melted butter into ingredients, beat for about 3 minutes or until mixture is well combine.
Pour mixture into your cake tin and bake for about 30 minutes or until cooked when tested with a skewer.
